data.description: This 3 BR 2 Bath home is located with easy access to 71B in Bella Vista. Upstairs has 1,566 Sq Ft with an additional 572 Sq Ft within the garage. Downstairs has 1,072 Sq Ft of living area, with an additional 476 Sq Ft of storage area. The deck was just replaced last month and several improvements have been made over the last five years.
